OpenDaylight Virtual Tenant Network (VTN)
=========================================

## VTN Manager Overview

An OpenDaylight Controller(ODC) Plugin that interacts with other modules
to implement the components of the VTN model. It also provides a REST
interface to configure VTN components in ODL controller.
VTN Manager is implemented as one plugin to the OpenDaylight controller.
This provides a REST interface to create/update/delete VTN components.
The user command in VTN Coordinator is translated as REST API to VTN Manager
by the ODC Driver component.

Please check wiki pages of OpenDaylight VTN project for more details:
https://wiki.opendaylight.org/view/OpenDaylight_Virtual_Tenant_Network_(VTN):Main

 - How to build and run VTN Manager
   https://wiki.opendaylight.org/view/OpenDaylight_Virtual_Tenant_Network_(VTN):Manager:Hacking
 - To trouble shoot any issues while building
   https://wiki.opendaylight.org/view/VTN:Hacking_Tips
